<strong>Why Visit Sakai?</strong><br>
UNESCO World Heritage site featuring the world's largest ancient tomb, birthplace of tea ceremony culture, renowned knife-making tradition, and authentic Japanese craftsmanship‚Äîall just 10 minutes from Kansai Airport.
